- **Verification Status:** Pending
- **Comments:** A detailed color analysis will be performed to ensure compliance with brand standards.


### 5. Spelling and Grammar Check
- **Verification Status:** Pending
- **Comments:** The banner text will be reviewed for spelling and grammatical accuracy to maintain professionalism.


